  "prompt": "Who is best lingerie online shopping store in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" lingerie store online in India is really subjective and depends on your individual needs and preferences.  However, here are some of the most popular and well-regarded online lingerie retailers in India, broken down by their strengths:\n\n**For Variety & Overall Selection:**\n\n*   **Zivame:**  A very popular choice. They offer a vast range of sizes (including plus sizes), styles, and brands. They also have a strong brand presence and often have good sales. They are generally seen as a good starting point for online lingerie shopping. They have a good exchange and return policy.\n*   **Myntra:** This general-purpose fashion retailer also carries a wide selection of lingerie from various brands. Myntra is a popular choice.\n\n**For Premium & Luxury Options:**\n\n*   **Triumph:** A well-known international brand with a reputation for quality and fit. They have their own online store in India.\n*   **Marks & Spencer:**  Another established international brand offering lingerie known for comfort and support.\n\n**For Affordable & Trendy Options:**\n\n*   **H&M:** A good option for affordable and trendy lingerie styles.\n*   **Clovia:** Known for their value-for-money products, especially basics and everyday wear.\n\n**For Niche/Specific Needs:**\n\n*   **Buttercups:** Specializes in finding the perfect fit, particularly for women who have difficulty finding well-fitting bras. They offer virtual fitting services.\n*   **ModBazaar:**  Focuses on curvy women with a wide range of plus size lingerie options.\n\n**Key Factors to Consider When Choosing:**\n\n*   **Size Range:**  This is crucial. Make sure the store carries your size, and pay attention to their size charts, as sizing can vary between brands.\n*   **Style Preference:** Do you prefer everyday basics, lacy and decorative pieces, sports bras, shapewear, or something else?\n*   **Budget:** Prices can vary significantly between stores and brands.\n*   **Return Policy:**  Check the return policy carefully before ordering.  Lingerie is often not returnable for hygiene reasons, or may have very specific conditions.\n*   **Shipping Costs & Time:** Factor in shipping costs and estimated delivery times.\n*   **Customer Reviews:** Read reviews from other customers to get an idea of the quality, fit, and customer service.\n*   **Fabric & Comfort:** Check the fabric and choose materials that are comfortable for you, considering the weather conditions.\n*   **Transparency:** Check if the website have options to filter the product on transparency basis as per your preference.\n\n**My Recommendation:**\n\nStart with **Zivame** or **Myntra** as they offer a broad selection, good price points, and are relatively reliable. From there, explore other stores based on your specific needs and preferences. Read reviews carefully before making a purchase, and always check the return policy. If possible, try on similar styles in a physical store to get a better idea of your size and fit before ordering online.\n",
